<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- لَا بِفَصْدٍ وَشَرْطٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَلَا إِنْ فَكَّرَ فَأَنْزَلَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا إِنْ فَعَلَ شيئًا مِنْ جَميعِ المُفَطِّرَاتِ نَاسِيًا أَوْ مُكْرَهًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَلَا إِنْ دَخَلَ مَاءُ مَضْمَضَةٍ أَوِ اسْتِنْشَاقٍ حَلْقَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَلَوْ بَالَغَ أَوْ زَادَ عَلَى ثَلَاثٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَلَا إِنْ دَخَلَ الذُّبَابُ أَوِ الغُبَارُ حَلْقَهُ بِغَيْرِ قَصْدٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَلَا إِنْ جَمَعَ رِيقَهُ فَابْتَلَعَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمَنْ جَامَعَ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- فِي نَهَارِ رَمَضَانَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- فِي قُبُلٍ أَوْ دُبُرٍ، وَلَوْ لِمَيْتٍ أَوْ بَهِيمَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- فِي حَالَةٍ يَلْزَمُهُ فِيهَا الإِمْسَاكُ، مُكْرَهًا كَانَ أَوْ نَاسِيًا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#006d98">لَزِمَهُ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> القَضَاءُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>